<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/25261633">「深夜主人公在少林寺偷窥大师兄练神功」如何神展开地续写？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2287253" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content"></div>


</div>
