<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$wangerxiaoshibendan" href="/people/wangerxiaoshibendan">王二小</a>，<strong title="(=ﾟДﾟ=) ▄︻┻┳━" class="zu-question-my-bio">(=ﾟДﾟ=) ▄︻┻┳━ </strong>

