<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="647">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$jia-yan-69" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/jia-yan-69" class="zg-link" title="佳言">佳言</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$li-zhuo-xin-88" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/li-zhuo-xin-88" class="zg-link" title="黎安">黎安</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$xu-jian-71-38" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/xu-jian-71-38" class="zg-link" title="许剑">许剑</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2287253" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">偷窥了很久，发现师兄看起来老了许多。<br><br>听到师兄悲切的念叨自己的名字，<br><br>我忽然想起来，<br><br>自己已经死掉很多年了。


</div>

</div>
